### Next Steps

To push these commits, you need to authenticate with GitHub using one of these options:

**Option 1 (Recommended):** Use GitHub CLI
```bash
gh auth login
git push -u origin master
```

**Option 2:** Configure git credentials
```bash
git config credential.helper store
git push -u origin master
```

**Option 3:** Switch to SSH
```bash
git remote set-url origin git@github.com:cletcher/chaprola-fitlog.git
git push -u origin master
```

All development work is complete - only the authentication setup is needed to sync with GitHub.
